import { Component, OnInit, ViewChild, HostListener } from '@angular/core';
import { Report, Status } from '../models/Report';
import { ReportService } from '../services/report.service';
import { UpVoteService } from '../services/upvote/up-vote.service';
import { cpus } from 'os';



@Component({
  selector: 'app-notificaties',
  templateUrl: './notificaties.component.html',
  styleUrls: ['./notificaties.component.css']
})
export class NotificatiesComponent implements OnInit {

  constructor( private reportService: ReportService, private upvoteService: UpVoteService) { }
  newInnerHeight;
  newInnerWidth ;
  @ViewChild('tabGroup', { static: true }) tabGroup;
  @ViewChild('tabGroup2', { static: true }) tabGroup2;
  isSubLoaded:Boolean;
  notifList = [];

  @HostListener('window:resize', ['$event'])
  onResize(event) {
    this.newInnerHeight = event.target.innerHeight;
    this.newInnerWidth = event.target.innerWidth;
    console.log(this.newInnerWidth);
  }


  ngOnInit() {
    this.newInnerWidth = window.innerWidth;
    this.getSubscribedReports();
  }


  getSubscribedReports(){
    this.reportService.getSubscribedReports().subscribe((res) => {
      if(res !== null && res.length > 0) {
        res.forEach(element => {
          if(element.status == Status.FINISHED){
            this.notifList.push(element);
          }
        }
          )
        this.isSubLoaded = true;
      } else {
        this.isSubLoaded = false;
      }
    });
  }

  removeNotification(report){
  this.notifList = this.notifList.filter(item => item != report);
  this.upvoteService.removeUserVote(report);
  }
}


<div [hidden]="!isSubLoaded">
            <div *ngIf='newInnerWidth >  500' class="header mt-3 mb-3">
            </div>
            <div class="mat-elevation-z8 mb-3 container">
                <br/>
                <h1 class="header">Notificaties</h1><br/>
                <div *ngFor='let n of notifList' class="status mb-1">
                    <h6>Het defect: <b>"{{n.title}}"</b> in lokaal <i>{{n.campus}} {{n.location}}</i> is <strong style="color:green;">voltooid</strong>. 
                    <button class= "icon" mat-icon-button color="warn" (click)='removeNotification(n)'>
                        <mat-icon>delete</mat-icon>
                      </button>  </h6>   

                </div>
                <br/>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div [hidden]="isSubLoaded !== undefined" class="container">
            <div class="spinner-border text-danger" role="status">
                <span class="sr-only">Loading...</span>
            </div>
</div>
